● Both fixes implemented in src/actor.rs:

  Proposal 9 — WriteAsync buffer lifetime (critical): Added read_buf and
  write_buf fields to PendingOp that pin Arc<DmaBuffer> / Arc<Mutex<DmaBuffer>>
  until the SPDK completion callback fires and the pending op is removed. This
  fixes both WriteAsync and ReadAsync (which had the same latent bug).

  Proposal 2 — ControllerReset scope (moderate): Extracted reset handling into
  handle_controller_reset(&mut self, requesting_client_id) on
  BlockDeviceHandler, which iterates ALL clients' pending ops and cancels them
  with Aborted errors before issuing the hardware reset. ControllerReset is now
  intercepted in poll_clients before reaching dispatch_command.

